title: Pumpkin Apple Pie Cider with Breville Juicer 800JEXL
description:
Pumpkin Apple Pie Cider with the Breville Juicer - 800JEXL
- ½ Cup Pumpkin flesh
-  3 large apples cored (we used Gala)
-  1 tablespoon Honey
-  1 teaspoon vanilla
-  ¼ teaspoon cinnamon
-  Dash of ground cloves
-  Dash of ground ginger
-  Dash of ground nutmeg
Juice pumpkin and Apples on high (can also use a blender) add vanilla
and spices, stir well. Enjoy!!

See the Breville Juicer 800JEXL at Abt: http://www.abt.com/product/18215/Breville-Juicer-Fountain-Elite-800JEXL.html?r=0&utm_source=youtube&utm_medium=video&utm_campaign=800JEXL_201701013
